author: @alkalinebase
text: This is just so comforting to hear him say that he was/is not sure what he wanted in life, because that is literally me. I don't think I've ever acknowledged that , not even now . I  have a masters in  biotechnology with a whole biology background like I didn't even know if I wanted to become a doctor, but now I have no hopes and aspirations of continuing in that field. Don't have a job, still live with my parents and have almost no idea what I will do in my life. All I ever did was study and maintain good marks in my life but now this is weird waters! I didn't get a seat through NEET,  2 times and then I gave up, tried giving govt. exams, but that was not for me. Didn't clear gate and I don't think I've enough memory cells left to think about CSIR-NET. I am honestly scared to admit that I don't love the subject I've studied all my life and just cannot deal with it anymore. I was exploring options and came across krish and I think this is something I would really love to do. I just stop wanting to feel like shit and a total loser! Going to give my last attempt of gate this year. I just hope I don't die before that. lol

author: @tarot-oo8ff
text: after my college I got placed in a marketing company worked there for 8 months with good perks but suddenly my father met with an accident and I lost my job bcz I was unable to leave him during his last days and after 1.5 years he succumbed to his injuries...after that my Bhabhi for the sake of property division got me and my mother arrested on false accusations of domestic violence for 2 years bcz of that I cud not give any exam or job interviews..when we got cleared from court cases..I left with no energy to do anything ... father's death loss ..and false court case made me to slip into depression..tried to commit suicide once but suddenly one line strike in my mind which my father used to say" death is for once..it's the easiest way to escape from life.. everybody have to die one day..but u have to live everyday before death...and life is all about struggle".Then I threw those pills ,open 1 food outlet of pizza in Delhi Mayur Vihar..I ran it successfully..there I met with some investors with the help of then open 3 others outlets in Delhi ..earned well..then I thought let's try my hand in civil service now..I cleared state pcs exam of Bihar..60-62nd bpsc and went till interview but just before interview I got news my elder brother died in car accident..and we were in debt of 150 Lacs in business...I cudn't cope up with my bro death heavy debt on head and again slipped into depression..sold almost all property and money I earned in busines..and now there is no debt on head ..so I thought let's try into data science and artificial intelligence and here I am..now my documents age does not allow me to give upsc or any other exam but i can give state pcs and I can clear that exam I know..but I left with no money..so my prime focus is first excel in this data science field earn a decent salary and I have good idea of business too this time but it's on hold...I LL do that later on first will earn money..for investment again..All I learnt from my life is ...life sucks,but it's all ur battle..u have to fight alone..so never give up....and yes ! I forgot to mention I am a girl.I had option to marry too but got stuck with one boy only ,trusted him thinking he loves me bcz we got engaged before my brother death..but he left me alone after his death when he heard we have 150 Lacs debt...my mother asked him if he is ready to marry me now ..he bluntly droped the idea of marriage with me..may be bcz he was expecting dowry from my side and he came to know i left with no money..so here I am following Krish Naik sir and ineuron team so that again I stand up and b that woman which I wanted to be not for the sake of marriage or getting married but to keep my life busy with decent salary and experience.
